# RepCheck

RepCheck is a tool designed to help track and analyze congressional representatives and legislation in the United States Congress.

## Features

- Track voting records of representatives
- Monitor current and pending legislation
- Search representatives by state and district
- View legislative progress and updates
- Analyze voting patterns
- Use AI to provide plain English explinations of legislation

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/repcheck.git

# Navigate to directory
cd repcheck

# Create virtual environment (optional) will be a docker container in the future
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use: venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

